name: Jantar Mantar
description: An astronomical observatory with architectural instruments featuring giant sundials, a cosmic calendar, and other cool astronomical tools. It's a UNESCO World Heritage Site.
address: J6G8+RMC, Connaught Place, Sansad Marg, New Delhi, Delhi 110001

name: City Palace
description: A sprawling complex of courtyards, gardens, and buildings that was the home of the maharajas of Jaipur. It is part museum and part palace, so you can see the royal apartments and a vast collection of artifacts
address: Gangori Bazaar, J.D.A. Market, Pink City, Jaipur, Rajasthan 302002
